13:09.120 --> 13:10.280
Okay.

13:13.170 --> 13:15.821
Honey, you have something
on your dress.

13:19.960 --> 13:21.996
Hey! What was that?

13:33.750 --> 13:36.708
Three more victims
with non-fatal wounds

13:36.710 --> 13:39.998
and it's only been 48 hours
since the last shooting.

13:40.000 --> 13:42.070
Media attention and the FBI presence

13:42.080 --> 13:45.072
