a gun to kill somebody.

16:01.750 --> 16:03.456
Well, the only truly
effective weapon we have

16:03.460 --> 16:06.031
is our ability to do
the one thing they can't.

16:06.040 --> 16:08.076
-Which is what?
-Empathize.

16:08.670 --> 16:11.707
They dehumanize their victims.
We humanize the killers.

16:11.710 --> 16:14.281
